# Supabase configuration for local development
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-api-key

# Optional: set a custom app origin for Supabase redirects
# VITE_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GEMINI_API_KEY — Supabase Edge Function Secret (NOT in this file)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Gemini API key is stored ONLY as a Supabase Edge Function secret.
# It is used by supabase/functions/copilot-insights/index.ts server-side.
# This ensures the key is never exposed to the browser bundle.
#
# To configure:
#   supabase secrets set GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Get a free key (no credit card needed):
#   https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY — Supabase Edge Function Secret (NOT in this file)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Anthropic API key is stored ONLY as a Supabase Edge Function secret,
# NOT in this .env file. This ensures the key is never exposed to the browser.
#
# To configure the Anthropic API key:
#
# 1. Via Supabase CLI (recommended):
#    supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# 2. Or via Supabase Dashboard:
#    - Go to Project Settings → Edge Functions → Secrets
#    - Click "New Secret"
#    - Name: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#    - Value: your-anthropic-api-key
#
# The edge function at supabase/functions/chat/index.ts will access this secret
# using Deno.env.get('ANTHROPIC_API_KEY')
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
